description: I heard about a nice lido outside of Prague so I decided to go hunting there. To my great disappointment the place was completely without water and there were no people around. No one besides two boys I found chilling out in a nearby forest. They came to the lido to have a nice swim and to sunbathe a bit. Instead they had to hide from the scorching sun under the trees. I had a little chat with them about their hobbies and girls but I could tell I was making them little nervous. When I offered the boys cash for nudity, they refused and I thought it was over. It turned out that they were just shy of each other. Once one of them left, the other one was much easier to work with. He wanted money and I had plenty opportunities for him to earn it. I wonder if his friend was watching us from bushes...
title: Czech Hunter 442
